{
  "stem": "964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They thought that we are Germans, but just dirty Germans that just came from work or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So-- and the other driver who took us into the Dneprodzerzhinsk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Was afternoon.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Afternoon, we came in into Dneprodzerzhinsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so many trucks, so many soldiers from different companies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Usually, the company occupied the town and this is the administration.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So everybody's the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you have some tank units people, from-- from [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what else, telephone, these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we start talking to the soldiers in the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did-- what happened?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're get the, oh, they told us in Zaporozh'e that the Russians attacked nighttime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We hardly got away with our pants on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a lot of them-- so-- and we start to find out other things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I say, how are you eating?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What-- where are you sleeping?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they told us they're going to the [NON-ENGLISH], this is the chief of the military.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he gives them a slip of paper to go to a particular place where they're getting food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they're having apartments that is to their disposition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they gave address to the apartments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they had where to sleep and where are they getting the food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We walked around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We are not Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What can we do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Just walking around like that, and you know, then we stop us for a paper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had no papers, nothing-- nothing, without anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This Jakob, [NON-ENGLISH], he looked like a German-- blond hair, blue eyes, and very like-- not aggressive, but he was-- you can see on his face he's not afraid.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'll Go into that [NON-ENGLISH], and I'm going to tell him a story that we are Poles.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
